cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH configuration index to 1000 exceeds the valid range (0-255), leading to improper PRACH configuration and RACH failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH 配置索引設定為 1000 超過有效範圍 (0-255)，導致 PRACH 配置不當，並造成 RACH 失敗。
